T02D2753:133b-0: @133b * // 'phags pa spyan ras gzigs dbang phyug mkha' spyod la phyag 'tshal lo //
T02D2753:133b-2: 'phags pa nam mkha'i spyod yul te //
T02D2753:133b-3: zhes 'byung ba'i sgrub thabs bshad par bya'o //
T02D2753:133b-4: srid las ring gyur shin tu 'phags pa'i skur bstan pa //
T02D2753:133b-5: zla ba ltar dkar ye shes thugs kyi padmo las //
T02D2753:133b-6: legs 'khrungs phyogs char dbyangs can nor rgyun rdo rje
T02D2753:133b-7: phag / sgrol ma rnam bzhi'i cod pan rin chen
T02D2753:133b-8: gyis btud rgyal // mtha' dang stong nyid chen po yi //
T02D2753:133b-9: rnal 'byor snying rje mchog gi ngang //
T02D2753:133b-10: skye ba med las skye ba'i dngos //
T02D2753:133b-11: 'phags pa thugs rje che bsgom bya //
T02D2753:133b-12: t'a la bdun srid nam mkha' yi //
T02D2753:133b-13: ngos la sna tshogs pad zla'i steng //
T02D2753:133b-14: bdag nyid rnam par shes kyi hra'i: //
T02D2753:133b-16: rim gyis padmo dkar nyid dang //
T02D2753:133b-17: de gyur pas ni mgon po nyid //
T02D2753:133b-18: g-yon zhabs 'khor los zla dbus mnan //
T02D2753:133b-19: g-yas zhabs gyen du cher bskyod pa'o //
T02D2753:133b-20: phyag g-yas padmo mdzes lcug sdug /'dab stong rnam par bye ba yi //
T02D2753:133b-21: sdong bu'i lcug ma 'khyud skyogs kyis //
T02D2753:133b-22: zhabs g-yas mkhrig ma bteg bsnams la //
T02D2753:133b-23: 'bar ba'i rin chen lhag ge ba'i //
T02D2753:133b-24: rgyan rnams kun gyis rab tu brgyan //
T02D2753:133b-25: bde chen rnam par mi rtog ngang //
T02D2753:133b-26: sbyin dang mi 'jigs rgyur bcas pa'o //
T02D2753:133b-28: 'di dag rang dang rjes su mthun pa'o //
T02D2753:133b-29: don bsgrubs 'od zer bsdu ba yi //
T02D2753:133b-30: sbyor bas shar la sogs pa yi //
T02D2753:133b-31: phyogs bzhi por ni lha mo bzhi //
T02D2753:133b-32: gangs ri ltar dkar blo bzangs 'ong mdzad ral gri pu sti g-yas dang g-yon //
T02D2753:134a-0: gser bzangs ltar ser nor mang yid 'ong nor bu @134a * //
T02D2753:134a-2: byi ru ltar dmar 'od mdzad gri gug mi mgo phyed khrag bkang //
T02D2753:134a-3: aindra'i mdog ljang gzhon nu sgeg mo skyabs sbyin autpal legs bsnams pa'o //
T02D2753:134a-4: de rjes ye shes dgug pa yi //
T02D2753:134a-5: cho ga mchod rgyas khyad par bzhis //
T02D2753:134a-6: mchod byas gus pa gsol ba yi//
T02D2753:134a-7: sngags brjod de nas sngags bzla'o //
T02D2753:134a-8: rjes mthun phrin las lnga po yis //
T02D2753:134a-9: mkha' khyab don kun bsgrubs nas ni //
T02D2753:134a-11: gyen du sbar ba'i rnal 'byor bya //
T02D2753:134a-12: yang ni phyogs bsdu dngos grub bslang //
T02D2753:134a-13: the tshom med bcas phrin las bzhi //
T02D2753:134a-14: lha bzhi rang gi rigs bzhin du //
T02D2753:134a-15: mkhas pas rjes su gzhug par bya //
